cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper deals with image quality and its impact on face detection and recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also uses deep neural networks for classification, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as it focuses on analyzing images of mixed qualities and adapting to real-world scenarios.
